rows.label: tev055501_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_SEL0011
rows.name:
Ask Tikotiko for his thoughts on
friendship treaties with xenoforms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Tikotiko about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0001
rows.name:
Nopon business booming ever since human friends
agreed to sign friendship treaty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0002
rows.name:
Bananaleaf from Noctilum so popular in city that
some Nopon in Dodonga Caravan sell enough in one
day to buy new house![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0003
rows.name: Tikotiko decide to move here to get in on action.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0004
rows.name:
But lots of Nopon have same idea, so city quickly
turning into merchant battleground.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0005
rows.name:
Tikotiko need to cook up get-rich-quick idea that
no other Nopon think of.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0008
rows.name:
Tikotiko decided to approach Ma-non named
Noborata to research hit products in city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0009
rows.name:
But Noborata still not return on investment.
All Noborata ever talk about is "cultural exchange."
...More like cultural rip-off! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0010
rows.name:
Tikotiko should have known better than to trust
lazy Ma-non. Maybe Tikotiko not cut out for
cutthroat business world after all...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Tikotiko about business.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Tikotiko about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0011
rows.name:
Everyone so eager to join BLADE, Tikotiko decide to
look into perks. Best not to leave any money on table![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0012
rows.name:
Sure enough, BLADEs get paid for lots of things!
Taking jobs at Mission Control... Setting data probes...
Punching enemies in face and then selling loot...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0013
rows.name:
But most profitable jobs usually come directly from
other friends who need assistance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0014
rows.name: Just like friend did for Min'barac.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0015
rows.name:
So basically, miserable people source of income for all
BLADE friends. Tikotiko never look at city same way
again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0018
rows.name:
Tikotiko totally 100 percent behind friends joining
BLADE and making easy money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0019
rows.name:
But why do friends have to keep digging into pockets
of Tikotiko?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0020
rows.name:
Selia want only most expensive weapons.
Nearly bankrupt poor Tikotiko![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0021
rows.name:
And Noborata taking out massive loan to develop
new gear![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055501_MSG0022
rows.name:
Tikotiko scared for future. Never knew biggest threat
to livelihood was going to be best friends...[ST:wait ]
